headline: Killing of Renee Good in Minneapolis reignites US debate over ICE
description: The 37-year-old mother was shot dead by an Immigration and Customs Enforcement agent while maneuvering her vehicle on a street on Wednesday. Footage of the incident, which does not confirm the self-defense claim put forward by the Trump administration, has sparked outrage across the United States.

headline: Iran protests swell nationwide as crackdown intensifies and internet is cut
description: The country saw the largest demonstrations in nearly two weeks, with rights groups reporting dozens of protesters killed.

headline: France enjoys another banner year for tourism, buoyed by campgrounds and international visitors
description: International tourism revenue rose by 9% in France in 2025, according to the United Nations World Tourism Organization.
